            <abstract>
                <p><foreign xml:lang="gez">Qǝne</foreign> without type indication in the manuscript. It has eight lines, meaning
                    that it can be classified as a <foreign xml:lang="gez">mawaddǝs qǝne</foreign> according to
                    <bibl><ptr target="bm:Guidi1900Qene"/></bibl>. 
                    In the first line, it refers to a "<foreign xml:lang="gez">Daǧǧāzmāčč</foreign> Wǝbe", possibly
                    <persName ref="PRS10100WebeAt"/>.
                    It is attributed to <persName ref="PRS14574GabraLeul" cert="high" corresp="SD">Gabra Lǝʿul</persName> 
                    in the manuscript.</p>
